A '''bowl of fish''' is a consumable item purchased from [[Mairin's Market]] found [[underwater]] beneath [[Fossil Island]]. Players can take out a variety of fish from it depending on the player's [[Fishing]] level, whereupon the bowl will be destroyed.

A bowl of fish will give an average of one of each kind of the following items: [[Raw shrimps|shrimps]], [[Raw anchovies|anchovies]], [[Raw sardine|sardine]], [[Raw tuna|tuna]], [[Raw lobster|lobster]], [[Raw swordfish|swordfish]], [[Raw sea turtle|sea turtles]] and [[Raw manta ray|manta rays]]. There is also a rare chance of receiving [[Fossil Island fossil|fossils]].

